# 🧠 NeuroTrackr – AI Health Monitoring Wearable

## 🚀 Overview

**NeuroTrackr** is a compact, AI-powered wearable device designed to monitor vital health parameters and detect early signs of critical conditions like stroke and seizures. It combines embedded systems, cloud computing, and intelligent analytics to provide real-time monitoring and alerts.

---

## 🎯 Features

* ❤️ ECG Monitoring (AD8232)
* 💓 Pulse & SpO2 Tracking (MAX30102)
* 🌡️ Body Temperature Monitoring (MAX30205)
* 📡 Real-time data transmission via ESP32-S3
* ☁️ Cloud-based monitoring dashboard
* 🤖 AI-based analysis and alert generation
* 🚨 Emergency alert system
* 🔋 Compact and wearable armband design

---

## 🧰 Components Used

### 🔌 Electronics

* ESP32-S3
* MAX30102 (Pulse & SpO2 Sensor)
* AD8232 (ECG Sensor)
* MAX30205 (Temperature Sensor)
* Li-ion Battery
* TP4056 Charging Module
* Optional GSM Module (SIM800L)

---

## ⚙️ System Architecture

```id="6wqg3p"
Sensors (ECG, SpO2, Temp)
        ↓
     ESP32-S3
        ↓
     Cloud Server
        ↓
   AI Analysis Engine
        ↓
     Alerts / Dashboard
```

---

## 🌐 Working Principle

* Sensors collect real-time physiological data
* ESP32 processes and transmits data to cloud
* AI analyzes patterns and detects abnormalities
* Alerts are triggered for emergency conditions
* Data is accessible via web/mobile dashboard

